title.rendered: Air Wisconsin Airlines Head Office: Ticket Booking and Fleet

content.rendered:
Air Wisconsin Airlines is a regional airline based at Appleton International Airport in the town of Greenville, Wisconsin, United States, near Appleton. Air Wisconsin previously operated US Airways Express service on behalf of US Airways prior to becoming an American Eagle regional air carrier. As of March 2018, Air Wisconsin operates exclusively as a United Express regional air carrier with primary hubs to located at Chicago O’Hare International Airport (ORD) and Washington Dulles International Airport (IAD).

 

 

Air Wisconsin Airlines Address: Air Wisconsin Airlines

W6390 Challenger Drive, Suite 203

Appleton, WI 54914

Phone Number : 920-739-5123

Air Wisconsin Airlines Official website: http://www.airwis.com/

Air Wisconsin Fleet

Bombardier CRJ-200

 Queries handled Air Wisconsin Airlines Customer care:

Schedule, eBooking, Rescheduling, Track and Trace, Charter Service Queries, Trucking service Queries, e-claims Flight Information, Missing Luggage, Delayed Flights. Pharma, pets, valuable, perishable goods and extra care shipment queries. MileagePlus

Is there any problem / complaint with reaching the Air Wisconsin Airlines Address or Phone number? Please report any issues using the below comment form.

Rate your experience with the Air Wisconsin Airlines : (click on the stars below)
